oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: 150th Anniversary of American Civil War: Tennessee
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Anniversaries; United States--History--Civil War, 1861-1865;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (blue and red on white) announcing the 150th Anniversary of the American Civil War in Tennessee. Poster features a woodcut of the state of Tennessee. Official poster of the Tennessee Sesquicentennial and produced by the Lotz House Foundation. Poster is the fourth in a series of four.
